        <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2019-08-10">
        <p itemprop="description">Had to stop here quick due to a noise coming from left front wheel. Zac the owner took it for a test drive and immediately afterward put it on the lift for a look.  Happened to be a loose caliper and wheel done by another auto shop I had it with the previous day for hub bearings replacement. Luckily I stopped in time for Zac to take care of or else a disaster could of happened.  Gave me a complete write up receipt for the charge so I could bring to the other shop. Thanks for taking me in right away Zac!<p>
    </div>

