 myself he told me he&amp;#39;s not doing the inspection.  I asked why not and he just replied with &amp;#34;no&amp;#34; and turned his back to me and walked away, no explanation whatsoever.<br&gt;<br&gt;I&amp;#39;ve been coming to this shop for a few years now getting common services done like oil changes, inspections, flat tire repair.  To have him refuse service to my car because I simply decided to change my own brakes instead of paying him is really unprofessional.  It&amp;#39;s not too big of a deal for me since there are hundreds of other shops who will do my inspection but there are 3 other vehicles in my household and you just lost our business for all our vehicles.","language":"en"},"rating":1,"photosUrl":"/biz_photos/flushing-tire-flushing?userid=yl578ShnBzdeJySPXpEO2g","feedback":{"counts":{"funny":1,"useful":1,"cool":1},"userFeedback":{"funny":false,"useful":false,"cool":false},"voterText":null},"business":{"alias":"flushing-tire-flushing","id":"MzWdy_beTpCKSo8QpwKUFg","name":"Flushing Tire"},"localizedDateVisited":null,"tags":[],"userId":"yl578ShnBzdeJySPXpEO2g","previousReviews":null,"photos":[],"id":"s_QiVN2SB_5Lm3GxkZgQSg","businessOwnerReplies":[{"comment":"Brandon I have no idea what are you talking about and I don’t remember talking to you about your brake rotors and if you had any issue you should’ve came back and  talk to me personally <br&gt;I’m in business to take care of customers not to turn away customers","owner":{"displayName":"Zack M.","role":"Business Owner","id":"cfLMbxoeNzRrZeG0nVMvrA","avatarSrc":"https://s3-media4.fl.yelpcdn.com/buphoto/AI5JT83sNg28JcWE9l1vsw/30s.jpg","avatarSrcSet":"https://s3-media4.fl.yelpcdn.com/buphoto/AI5JT83sNg28JcWE9l1vsw/90s.jpg 3.00x,https://s3-media4.fl.yelpcdn.com/buphoto/AI5JT83sNg28JcWE9l1vsw/ss.jpg 1.33x"},"id":"ZTk0Cayit7HRtZW7Jeu3qQ","localizedDate":"5/29/2019"}],"isUpdated":false,"user":{"src":"https://s3-media2.fl.yelpcdn.com/assets/srv0/yelp_styleguide/514f6997a318/assets/img/default_avatars/use